Class AbstractLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.openjpa.lib.log.AbstractLog

    Log
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LogFactoryImpl.LogImpl
    public abstract class AbstractLog
extends Object

    A simple implementation of the Log interface. Writes output to stdout.
